 of power, and, for a limited time, a discount that brings it down way below its original retail price. Grab it from Amazon while you can and save nearly 30% on the Galaxy Tab A9+, dropping it down to just $160. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-samsung-galaxy-tab-a9\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Samsung Galaxy Tab A9+?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Samsung Galaxy Tab A9+ has a lot going for it, thanks to a fantastic combination of features that you won\u0026#39;t find on any other tablet at this price. You get an 11-inch screen that delivers vibrant colors and excellent performance thanks to its 90Hz refresh rate, along with a powerful Qualcomm Snapdragon 695 chip that can handle pretty much anything that you can throw at it. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThis particular model that\u0026#39;s on sale comes with 4GB of RAM and also 64GB of internal storage. If the latter isn\u0026#39;t enough, you can always \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-microsd-cards/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eupgrade the storage using a microSD card\u003c/a\u003e, with support for up to 1TB. The tablet also has an 8MP camera on the rear, along with a 5MP camera on the front. You also get a quad speaker setup that delivers fantastic sound.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003ePerhaps most important is that Samsung also provides a great software experience as 